# NODE-FORM

- Node Farm is a simple product showcase application developed using Node.js, where the backend and frontend work together.
The project aims to teach the concept of server-side rendering using pure Node.js without relying on any external framework.

# Preview

![](/nodeform.gif)

# # Project Features

- It consists of a product listing and a product detail page.
- Modular code structure
- Responsive and modern UI
- JSON-based data management

# #  Technologies Used

# # Backend

- Node.js
- http 
- fs 
- url 
- Custom Template Engine
- JSON

# # Frontend

- HTML
- CSS3
- Google Fonts
- Emoji-based UI

# # Development Tools

- Nodemon
- Postman






